{"tid":569853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Steve Jobs 18歲應徵表格下月拍賣    料值39萬","createTime":"2018-02-23T05:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T05:18:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1b0cab752b54497d08cab7d430b9a4cd60ebaf","tid":569853,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180223/s00010/895f5800f4646b517c8dc9c8bae70724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180223%2Fs00010%2F895f5800f4646b517c8dc9c8bae70724.jpg&h=50526b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明日便是蘋果公司創辦人喬布斯（Steve Jobs）的生忌，日前波士頓拍賣行RR Auction稱，將於下月拍賣喬布斯於40多年前填寫的就業申請表，該文件目前估價為5萬美元（約39萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據該文件，喬布斯於1973年申請就業，當時18歲的他已渴望從事技術與設計相關的工作。今天世人認識教主名字是Steve Jobs，但當年初出茅蘆的他仍是寫上自己全名「Steven jobs」，但當中仍有少許錯漏，例如地址填上「reed college」。里德學院（Reed College）為喬布斯的母校，是位於俄勒岡州的一所私立文理學院。<br />\n<br />\n該就業申請表未有顯示喬布斯申請什麼職位，但他在「Special Abilities」（特別技能）一欄中，填寫「electronics tech or design engineer. digital.&mdash;from Bay near Hewitt-Packard」（電子技術或設計工程師，數碼&mdash;來自惠普附近的灣區），相信是指加州的科技先驅企業惠普。<br />\n<br />\n在填寫該表格大約三年後，喬布斯便與朋友沃茲涅克（Steve Wozniak）創立了蘋果，其於2011年因癌症去世，享年56歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1519360140605&amp;issue=20180223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1519360140605%26issue%3D20180223&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ0ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cc886709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1519360140605%26issue%3D20180223&h=72b83722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1519360140605&amp;issue=20180223</a>"},{"pid":"43ff725b6930b34e9ad97635a95e962fe7b3a3d2","tid":569853,"uid":142313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"佢支牙刷可能仲值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23169f4eb2ed2d4e14b9c7bc6cb376c5d428cc13","tid":569853,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"咁都有得炒....."},{"pid":"72b84f683d483e77800a94b2ff908631c2439a1d","tid":569853,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T05:18:38.000Z","msg":"分分鐘底褲都有得拍賣"}]}